<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="hosting-class-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1>Join a free hosting class</h1>
      <p class="lead">Learn from experienced hosts and become a successful host</p>
      <p>Our free classes cover everything you need to know to get started and grow your hosting business.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign up for a class</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>What you'll learn</h2>
        
        <div class="learning-cards">
          <div class="learning-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Getting started</h3>
            <p>Learn how to create your listing, set your price, and prepare your space for guests.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="learning-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-star"></i> 5-star hospitality</h3>
            <p>Discover how to provide exceptional experiences that earn great reviews.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="learning-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Guest communication</h3>
            <p>Master the art of communicating with guests from booking to checkout.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="learning-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> Pricing strategies</h3>
            <p>Learn how to set competitive prices and maximize your earnings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Class formats</h2>
        <div class="format-cards">
          <div class="format-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-video"></i> Live online classes</h3>
            <p>Interactive sessions with experienced hosts where you can ask questions in real-time.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>60-90 minute sessions</li>
              <li>Small group sizes</li>
              <li>Q&A sessions</li>
              <li>Recorded replay available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="format-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i> On-demand videos</h3>
            <p>Watch pre-recorded classes at your own pace, whenever it's convenient for you.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Watch anytime, anywhere</li>
              <li>Pause and rewind as needed</li>
              <li>Topic-specific modules</li>
              <li>Downloadable resources</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="format-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> In-person workshops</h3>
            <p>Join local meetups and workshops in your area to connect with other hosts.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Face-to-face networking</li>
              <li>Local market insights</li>
              <li>Hands-on activities</li>
              <li>Community building</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Upcoming classes</h2>
        <div class="class-schedule">
          <div class="class-item">
            <div class="class-date">
              <span class="day">15</span>
              <span class="month">Jul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="class-details">
              <h3>Getting Started: Create Your First Listing</h3>
              <p class="class-time">2:00 PM - 3:30 PM IST</p>
              <p class="class-instructor">Instructor: Sarah Johnson, Superhost</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="class-item">
            <div class="class-date">
              <span class="day">18</span>
              <span class="month">Jul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="class-details">
              <h3>5-Star Hospitality: Exceed Guest Expectations</h3>
              <p class="class-time">4:00 PM - 5:30 PM IST</p>
              <p class="class-instructor">Instructor: Michael Chen, Superhost</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="class-item">
            <div class="class-date">
              <span class="day">22</span>
              <span class="month">Jul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="class-details">
              <h3>Pricing Strategies: Maximize Your Earnings</h3>
              <p class="class-time">3:00 PM - 4:30 PM IST</p>
              <p class="class-instructor">Instructor: Emily Rodriguez, Superhost</p>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Register</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Why join a hosting class?</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Learn from experts:</strong> Our instructors are experienced Superhosts with proven track records</li>
          <li><strong>Get practical tips:</strong> Real-world advice you can apply immediately to your listing</li>
          <li><strong>Ask questions:</strong> Get answers to your specific hosting challenges</li>
          <li><strong>Connect with community:</strong> Meet other hosts and build your network</li>
          <li><strong>Stay updated:</strong> Learn about the latest features and best practices</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What hosts are saying</h2>
        <div class="testimonials">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"The hosting class gave me the confidence to start hosting. I learned so much about pricing and communication!"</p>
            <p class="testimonial-author">- Priya S., New Host</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial">
            <p>"Even after hosting for a year, I picked up great tips that improved my reviews and bookings."</p>
            <p class="testimonial-author">- James M., Experienced Host</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Ready to learn?</h3>
          <p>Sign up for a free class today and start your hosting journey.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Browse classes</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Can't make a live class?</h3>
          <p>Watch on-demand videos at your convenience.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Watch videos</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Hosting resources</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/hosting-resources">Resource Center</a></li>
            <li><a href="/community-forum">Community forum</a></li>
            <li><a href="/hosting-responsibly">Hosting responsibly</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Already a host?</h3>
          <p>Share your expertise by becoming a class instructor.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Become an instructor</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
